- Move the mouse cursor over a name to see more information.

a.title: ― ConceptualVariable: A variable at the highest level of abstraction.
a.xlink:title: ― ConceptualVariable: A variable at the highest level of abstraction.

a.title: ― Universe: Specialized unit type, with the specialization based upon characteristics other than time and geography.

a.title: ― Unit: Individual object of interest for some statistical activity, such as data collection.

a.title: ― InternationalString: Packaging structure for multiple language versions of the same string content. The language designation goes on the individual String ...
